# Atom-Z-Future syntax (Beta version)

A futuristic atom theme inspired by a design, [Evio online code editor](https://material.uplabs.com/posts/evio-online-code-editor), which I randomly came across. This is the beta version, if you find any bugs please report them on git and feel free to contribute as well. âœŒðŸ¼
